title: Do Bobby And Brantley Gilbert Have A Feud? + Who's Eating The Chocolate Covered Cicada? + Brett Eldredge Performs An Unreleased Song In Our Studio!
itunes:title: Do Bobby And Brantley Gilbert Have A Feud? + Who's Eating The Chocolate Covered Cicada? + Brett Eldredge Performs An Unreleased Song In Our Studio!
description:
Bobby talks about how listeners informed him something about Brantley Gilbert’s new song that leads him to wonder if they should have a beef. We even bring in our big boss to talk about it. We spin the wheel to see who has to eat a chocolate covered cicada. Brett Eldredge stops by to perform and talk about his new tour.
